Note on data:
Simulation outputs derived from public 국가중점데이터 cadastral datasets
(토지특성정보 AL_D194, 용도별건물정보 AL_D198 — 국토교통부 / data.go.kr)
inherit the source license terms: 공공누리 제1유형 (Korea Open Government
License Type 1 — Source attribution required). Please cite both this project
and the original data providers when redistributing derived outputs.
